rows.label: qev087404_MSG0001
rows.name: This is a huge help! Now we can get that armor patched up.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087404_MSG0002
rows.name: By the way, where's Commander Vandham?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087404_MSG0003
rows.name: Oh, he took off a while back.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087404_MSG0004
rows.name: WHAT? He didn't even stick around?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087404_MSG0005
rows.name:
Yeah, he seemed busy.
Said he had something else to take care of.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087404_MSG0006
rows.name:
And after Tatsu go to all that trouble
of finding stupid materials...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087404_MSG0009
rows.name: Don't worry, it's not your fault.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087404_MSG0010
rows.name: Oh, but he did leave a message for you guys.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087404_MSG0011
rows.name:
"Come see how I work at night.
And yeah, that's an order."[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087404_MSG0013
rows.name: Tatsu already ready to go home and sleep![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087404_MSG0014
rows.name: Well, we've come this far. Might as well see this through.[ST:wait ]
